# Modal + Layered Architecture Rule

- Any new modal or modal enhancement must use Global Modal Manager.
- Define or reuse a key in `components/modal-manager/modalKeys.ts`.
- Implement modal UI in `components/modal-manager/modals/*`.
- Mount modal components only in `components/modal-manager/ModalHost.tsx`.
- Add `data-modal-key` on opener actions in pages/components.
- Do not introduce new page-local modal state for long-term features.
- Keep UI -> Store/UseCase -> Service -> Firebase flow; no direct Firestore access in UI.
- Update `MODAL_MIGRATION_TRACKER.md` when migrating modal keys.

